name "have still not managed to pull the society towards complete acceptance of women in these roles"
target "https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/00220388.2022.2032671"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
 Thus, even if women get empowered by starting an agro-input shop, they
 still struggle to continue doing well in the business, expand their sales
 or secure financial support for renovations or further development of their
 shops.
 These concerns make us skeptical about the presence of 
